OL,7,FA police officer who kicked his wife
OL,8,Fdown the stairs and left her with a
OL,9,Fbroken back has been jailed.
OL,11,FHuw Orphan, who was a police constable
OL,12,Fwith Gwent Police at the time of the
OL,13,Fincident, had been arguing with his
OL,14,Fpolice officer wife Amy Burley by text
OL,15,Fmessage before the attack in April
OL,16,F2020.
