OL,7,FOrphan, 31, had denied inflicting
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,9,Fclaiming that he had not meant to make
OL,10,Fcontact with his partner nor cause her
OL,11,Fany harm but was instead trying to
OL,12,F"jump" up the stairs to put some
OL,13,Fdistance between the rowing pair when
OL,14,Fhis leg accidentally made contact with
OL,15,Fher.
