OL,7,FA jury at Cardiff Crown Court found
OL,8,Fthe defendant not guilty of the charge
OL,9,Fof causing grievous bodily harm with
OL,10,Fintent but found him guilty of the
OL,11,Flesser charge of causing grievous
OL,12,Fbodily harm. He was also found guilty
OL,13,Fof causing actual bodily harm during a
OL,14,Fseparate incident before the couple
OL,15,Fmoved to Barry.
OL,17,FHe has now been jailed for two years
OL,18,Fand six months.
