OL,7,FIn his evidence, Orphan told the jury
OL,8,Fhis relationship with fellow officer
OL,9,FAmy Burley began in April or May 2018
OL,10,Fbefore they married and moved in
OL,11,Ftogether in a house his wife was
OL,12,Frenting in Newport the following
OL,13,Fsummer.
OL,15,FThe jury was told the couple's
OL,16,Frelationship was initially "very
OL,17,Fpositive" but changed over time. By
OL,18,Fthe time the couple moved to a house
OL,19,Fin Barry in February 2020, Orphan
OL,20,Fdescribed the relationship as "in
OL,21,Ftatters".
