OL,7,FThe court heard the altercation took
OL,8,Fplace in the early hours of April 8,
OL,9,F2020, when PC Orphan got home from
OL,10,Fworking a late shift, with the couple
OL,11,Fexchanging texts during the evening.
OL,13,FGiving evidence, Orphan accepted he
OL,14,F"probably could and should have done
OL,15,Fmore to take the heat out of the
OL,16,Fargument".
