OL,7,FOrphan was also questioned about an
OL,8,Fincident which happened before the
OL,9,Fcouple moved to Barry. During the
OL,10,Fincident, Orphan was found to have
OL,11,Fassaulted his partner by grabbing her
OL,12,Fand taking her to the floor following
OL,13,Fa row about sterilising baby bottles.
OL,14,FHe claimed he did this only to
OL,15,F"neutralise the risk to me, to her,
OL,16,Fand to the children".
OL,18,FOn receiving the verdict, Judge Tracey
OL,19,FLloyd-Clarke thanked the jury for
OL,20,Ftheir time, adding: "We simply could
OL,21,Fnot do this without you."
