OL,7,F"My thoughts go out to the victim in
OL,8,Fthis case who has shown tremendous
OL,9,Fcourage in coming forward. There is no
OL,10,Fplace in our organisation or in our
OL,11,Fcommunities for perpetrators of
OL,12,Fdomestic violence and these actions do
OL,13,Fnot represent the values of the vast
OL,14,Fmajority of our hard-working and
OL,15,Fcommitted staff, many of whom work
OL,16,Ftirelessly to prevent and detect
OL,17,Fserious offences like these.
