OL,7,F"I know this case will have had a
OL,8,Fdetrimental impact on the trust and
OL,9,Fconfidence that victims of domestic
OL,10,Fabuse feel in coming forward to report
OL,11,Fto us. I want anyone considering doing
OL,12,Fso to know that we remain dedicated to
OL,13,Fsupporting survivors of domestic abuse
OL,14,Fand bringing offenders to justice for
OL,15,Fthese awful crimes.
OL,17,F"I would urge anyone who is suffering
OL,18,Fabuse to please get in touch with the
OL,19,Fpolice or another support service.
OL,20,FPlease don't suffer in silence."
